Description: Telegram CLI - terminal Telegram client
 TDLib + Rust daemon + TUI/CLI — a full-featured Telegram client
 for the terminal. Features include message management, channel
 monitoring, file operations, and a ratatui-powered TUI interface.
 .
 Commands: tg (CLI + TUI), tgcd (daemon)
 Communicates over Unix socket with LengthDelimitedCodec framing.
